Package: mlogtail
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, curl
Suggests: postfix
Description: Postfix mail server log monitoring with HTTP API
 mlogtail is a tool for monitoring Postfix mail server by reading log files
 and counting various mail delivery parameters. It provides both traditional
 socket interface and modern HTTP API with JSON responses.
 .
 Features:
  * Real-time log monitoring with automatic log rotation handling
  * HTTP API with JSON responses for modern monitoring systems
  * Traditional Unix/TCP socket interface for Zabbix integration
  * Automatic counter initialization from existing log files
  * Systemd integration with automatic log rotation synchronization
  * Built-in Postfix queue size monitoring